# Installation

Install [Apache Commons Daemon](http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-daemon/jsvc.html)
> sudo apt-get install jsvc

Install [Pi4J](http://pi4j.com/)
> curl -s get.pi4j.com | sudo bash

